Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.80,0:01:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.12,0:01:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真差劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.52,0:01:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,涉那小子一点都没进步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.33,0:02:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.11,0:02:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.54,0:02:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让开路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点 要过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.42,0:02:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好看着 最强的车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.81,0:02:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厉害 太帅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.05,0:02:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁都不能模仿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.39,0:02:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题 过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.65,0:02:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弯道出口会遇到对向车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.02,0:02:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让出内线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.03,0:02:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下个弯没有对向车 留五厘米 很多沙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.32,0:03:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚好 开得不错 状态非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.26,0:03:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样的话遇到谁都不会输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.12,0:03:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(135,256)\fs20\fad(650,750)}碓冰山道的天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.53,0:03:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.91,0:03:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次见面的女孩会突然给你电话号码?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.53,0:03:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁相信啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.94,0:03:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肯定是哪里弄错了 弄错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.34,0:03:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊 池谷前辈 没那么简单的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.80,0:03:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就以我来说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像我这样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.46,0:03:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车手不需要女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.85,0:03:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关键是没弄错的话就不像池谷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.96,0:03:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不像我是什么意思啊? 健二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.06,0:03:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就那么蠢吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不是这个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.05,0:03:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可照你说的也太顺利了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.32,0:04:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌啊 你们那种妒忌别人幸福的表现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.90,0:04:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那随风飘动的棕色长发...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.42,0:04:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回头看我时 那双水汪汪的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.43,0:04:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想她一定是神为了奖励认真工作的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.03,0:04:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而派来人间的天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.74,0:04:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天星期日 去轻井沢见真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.90,0:04:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工作 工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.23,0:04:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说 我们也悄悄跟在后面看看那女孩到底什么样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.63,0:04:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去啊 去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.03,0:04:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去亲眼看清楚到底是什么样的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.42,0:04:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 被池谷前辈发现了怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.33,0:04:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别担心 以现在池谷的状态不可能发现吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.83,0:04:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好看清楚传说中的真子到底长什么样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.34,0:04:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别妨碍池谷哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.97,0:05:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会妨碍他的 前辈被甩时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.16,0:05:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们会和他一起哭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是火热的友情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.14,0:05:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说他被甩...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.72,0:05:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正真人肯定没他说的那么可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.69,0:05:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙喜欢大惊小怪 自以为是得很
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.92,0:05:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说的是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我记得是在中学时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.47,0:05:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一次和他去秋名湖钓鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.73,0:05:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们俩一条鱼都没钓到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.35,0:05:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快要回去时 我终于钓到一条小鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.02,0:05:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后池谷那家伙就兴奋地大喊“哇 好大”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.52,0:05:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实才这么大...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.76,0:06:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知情的大叔们还特地跑来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.01,0:06:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时真是羞死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.07,0:06:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷真是个大惊小怪的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,健二前辈 旁边旁边...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.99,0:06:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕 说得入神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.35,0:06:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下意识地右脚用力...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.91,0:06:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本打算跟踪 结果却追上他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.46,0:06:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 池谷 原谅我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.64,0:06:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只想来看看真子长什么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.55,0:06:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的只是为了这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.05,0:06:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全没想过要妨碍你约会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.72,0:06:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别生气哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.62,0:06:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们会在下个出入口掉头的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.11,0:06:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真没办法 不回去也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.39,0:06:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不介意介绍给你们认识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.67,0:06:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.44,0:06:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.57,0:06:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...之后就别再跟来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的会生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.17,0:06:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.82,0:06:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.11,0:07:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些家伙是我的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.56,0:07:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次见面 我叫佐藤真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.89,0:07:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.36,0:07:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们在做梦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.82,0:07:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起来不像做梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.80,0:07:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我受了好大的打击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.76,0:07:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么池谷会和那么可爱的女孩...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.68,0:07:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车手不需要女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.08,0:07:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,健二前辈 一起哭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.57,0:07:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.95,0:07:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说我找不到女朋友?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.31,0:08:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 开玩笑的 玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.68,0:08:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那接下来我们怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.09,0:08:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这时候的轻井沢可不合适三个大男人溜达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如去碓冰山道看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.44,0:08:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子你喜爱什么样的车?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.92,0:08:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谈不上喜爱...以前向往过前一代的RX7
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.62,0:08:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,FC啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.75,0:08:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很雅致的爱好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.83,0:08:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷先生是车手吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.16,0:09:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过今天打算和普通驾驶员一样兜兜风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.68,0:09:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问...真子...这个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.74,0:09:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对男人当车手有什么看法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.84,0:09:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不错啊 因为我也喜欢车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.98,0:09:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.15,0:09:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车手果然比普通人开得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.45,0:09:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好车子有钱就能买到 但技术是买不回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.55,0:09:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得应变技术好的人比开昂贵外国车的人更帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.17,0:09:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好女孩 理想的女孩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.88,0:09:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是碓冰山道吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.53,0:10:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是第一次开 比想象中更困难的迂回道路啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.13,0:10:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.52,0:10:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样全都是弯道 路面又狭窄...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.46,0:10:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和秋名比起来似是而非啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.82,0:10:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在碓冰最快的不知道是谁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.10,0:10:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问...池谷先生...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.43,0:10:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.19,0:10:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从男人的角度看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.21,0:10:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你对喜欢山道 做出像车手般举动的女孩...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.49,0:10:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么看法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.65,0:10:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sil-80?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.05,0:10:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 听闻蓝色的Sil-80是现在最快的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.86,0:10:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外别吃惊哦 那车手是女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.74,0:10:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.80,0:10:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女车手吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.51,0:10:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不错啊 完全没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.89,0:11:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再好不过 感觉女车手反而能有共同语言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.31,0:11:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.83,0:11:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此 明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.41,0:11:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子想成为车手 所以向往的车会是FC
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.72,0:11:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女孩开的Sil-80啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.15,0:11:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问 Sil-80是...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.36,0:11:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外国车吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.41,0:11:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.81,0:11:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sil-80就是180配上Silvia前脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.47,0:11:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是Silvia和180的结合版所以叫Sil-80
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.06,0:11:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个车手是碓冰山道最快的车手 而且还是个女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.40,0:11:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真想见识见识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.80,0:11:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等到晚上的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.42,0:11:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该能在碓冰山道见到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.89,0:11:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过还是千万别和她比赛的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.58,0:11:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为本地都没人能赢她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.21,0:12:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秋名SPEED STARS就是我组建的车队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.32,0:12:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在被称为秋名最快的车手就在我们队里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.66,0:12:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我的后辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.56,0:12:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,论速度的话 接下来就是我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.78,0:12:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了? 真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.75,0:12:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.29,0:12:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 好像都在说车的事 很无聊吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.72,0:12:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 没这回事 我也非常喜欢车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.87,0:12:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.76,0:12:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗...那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.74,0:12:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.89,0:12:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子难道也是因为漂移的魅力才向往成为车手的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.52,0:12:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没我这点水平的话很难掌握的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.59,0:12:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为这是很危险的技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.45,0:12:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷先生你也很擅长漂移?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.43,0:12:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.56,0:12:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.29,0:13:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你 今天很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.65,0:13:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问 真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.93,0:13:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.75,0:13:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问 真子...这个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.79,0:13:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你现在交往的人...这个...有吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.29,0:13:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.16,0:13:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以...请再打电话给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.00,0:13:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.86,0:13:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷 听得见吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.05,0:13:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷前辈 醒醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.81,0:13:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们还在啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.55,0:14:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里 太担心前辈了所以想回去也没回成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.58,0:14:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样? 顺利吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.59,0:14:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天真是个好日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.89,0:14:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就去吃饭吧 我好久没请客了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.91,0:14:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顺便去瞧瞧碓冰的车手是怎么跑的 也不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.87,0:14:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来似乎进展顺利呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.71,0:14:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇迹这东西还真有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.80,0:14:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不错啊 碓冰所有车手水平都很高啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.00,0:14:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.60,0:14:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是第一次来秋名以外的山道吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.45,0:14:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感觉如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.69,0:14:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.41,0:14:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没亲手握着方向盘 所以不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.83,0:14:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗? 可看你用特别认真的眼神盯着弯道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.14,0:14:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.80,0:14:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和现在的眼神完全不一样哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本不像同一个人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.28,0:15:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样? 能跑吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.13,0:15:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种事不跑怎么知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.87,0:15:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.88,0:15:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sil-80吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.45,0:15:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连续逆漂移!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害 很高明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.79,0:15:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才的看到了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.02,0:15:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狭窄的道路上仍然迫力十足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.57,0:15:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然很得意地和真子说自己擅长漂移
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.85,0:15:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实连甩尾都害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.18,0:15:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样下去可不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.87,0:15:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再不认真努力的话 难得的天使就会离我而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这样下山回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.32,0:15:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.95,0:15:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管哪里的路上都有厉害的家伙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.11,0:16:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷那家伙特别拼命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.50,0:16:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里可是乘了三人 追不上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离远点比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.44,0:16:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感觉节奏有点问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.30,0:16:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷前辈的车开得很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.60,0:16:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种事你也看得出来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.83,0:16:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是很肯定 可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然失控了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.39,0:16:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和拓海说的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.88,0:16:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好 有对向车要来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.28,0:16:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真危险 真是的 哪来的笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.44,0:16:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害怕车尾太靠外就松了油门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.70,0:17:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像不忘找零的乡巴佬一样土得掉渣的初学者侧滑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.98,0:17:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托 13的小哥 不快点让开的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别的车陆续上来会很危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.33,0:17:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在就让
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.45,0:17:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷前辈也太丢脸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.58,0:17:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,丑死了 装作不认识吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.52,0:17:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很抱歉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.61,0:17:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.63,0:17:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.85,0:17:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碓冰山道最快的Sil-80的车手竟然是真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.56,0:17:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想死的心都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.38,0:18:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请假?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.56,0:18:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,电话也不接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.72,0:18:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个超认真工作的池谷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.27,0:18:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天的事对他打击很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.51,0:18:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那以后都没说过话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.12,0:18:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,服务区上厕所时也处于呆滞状态 眼神空洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.78,0:18:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很凄惨地一句话都不和我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.61,0:18:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早有不祥预感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.24,0:18:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女孩做池谷的女朋友实在可爱得过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.62,0:18:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正车手不需要女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.72,0:18:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤独车手树 这就是我的座右铭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.65,0:18:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望能早点走出阴影啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.86,0:18:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,浩一郎 电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.98,0:18:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想接 就说我睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.39,0:18:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正多半是健二吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.77,0:19:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是女孩哦 叫佐藤真子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.30,0:19:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说有话和我说...说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.67,0:19:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想戏弄我的话 就适可而止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.21,0:19:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的 戏弄什么的怎么可能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.40,0:19:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然驾驶着那么厉害的车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.42,0:19:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看到了 那辆Sil-80厉害的漂移
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.56,0:19:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你被称为碓冰最快吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.98,0:19:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那么厉害 至少也透露一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.49,0:19:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.39,0:19:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没打算隐瞒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.74,0:19:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天的事我也受了打击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.07,0:19:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我觉得必须说出实情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实情?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.97,0:20:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实我性格很保守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.80,0:20:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保守? 难以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能做出那么华丽漂移的人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.07,0:20:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个...有些人一握方向盘人格就会改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.63,0:20:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是那种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.21,0:20:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使跑得再快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.38,0:20:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人也不会把我看作恋爱对象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.81,0:20:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多也该结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.22,0:20:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.27,0:20:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今年夏天结束后就不做车手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.31,0:20:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为车手日子里最后夏天的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.26,0:20:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请让我和秋名的86在碓冰山道比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.62,0:20:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是我的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.72,0:20:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能成全我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.63,0:20:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.26,0:20:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把处女献给池谷先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.82,0:20:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 别说出那种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.82,0:20:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想和我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.28,0:20:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是这个意思 那家伙是我的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.10,0:21:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做不出这种像交易一般的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.94,0:21:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彻底明白了 真子真正的目的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.97,0:21:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并不是我 而是拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.98,0:21:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.35,0:21:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不然这么可爱的女孩怎么会对我感兴趣呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.77,0:21:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了 我尽力而为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.58,0:21:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.56,0:21:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但别误会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.17,0:21:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我并不是为了报答而帮你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.71,0:21:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.20,0:21:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想完成你的心愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.88,0:21:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.53,0:21:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然时间很短
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.51,0:21:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我真的很喜欢真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.43,0:22:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要真子高兴 那就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.43,0:22:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被别人听见的话 一定会笑我是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.46,0:22:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的很喜欢她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.76,0:22:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算一厢情愿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.35,0:22:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还是喜欢她
